{
  "page": "Feature quote/209",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“The gods made our bodies as well as our souls, is it not so? They gave us voices, so we might worship them with song. They gave us hands, so we might build them temples. And they gave us desire, so we might mate and worship them in <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">that way</a>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Chataya\" title=\"Chataya\">Chataya</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260408122432\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 70/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 304/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.657      1 -total\n100.00%    5.657      1 Template:Ref\n 66.82%    3.780      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26369-0!canonical and timestamp 20260408122432 and revision id 240815\n -->\n",
